            <span class="text-red-700 font-semibold">
              <Icon name="bolt" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Same-Day Service
              Available
            </span>
          </div>
          <h1
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight text-[#333333]"
          >
            Need Cleaning <span class="text-red-600">TODAY</span> in Birmingham?
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Unexpected guests? Last-minute showing? UAB event tonight? Don't
            stress - our same-day cleaning service gets your Homewood, Vestavia
            Hills, or Mountain Brook home immaculate fast. No rush fees, no
            emergency charges.
          </p>

          <div
            class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg border-2 border-red-200 mb-6"
