              <Icon name="venus" class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-1" /> Women-Led
            </span>
            <span
              class="bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm"
            >
              <Icon
                name="star"
                class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-1"
                fill="currentColor"
